Script info:
  description: Downloads the installer script for the logged in user

---
# Log in to Platform API
Get token:
  endpoint: ${digitalaiStaging}
Http endpoint: ${output}

---
Http GET:
  path: /workload/v1/cloud_connector/installer
  save as: install-cloud-connector.sh

Print: Extract installation files by running 'bash install-cloud-connector.sh'.
